**********flySim*************
=============================
A flight simulator that would be connected
to an Arduino and accelerometer for control.

Requirements:-
1. Arduino software
2. Python 
3. Panda3D

Instructions:-
1. Upload the arduino.ino sketch to the arduino board.
2. Connect x and y pin of accelerometer to pin A0 and A1.
3. Run 'ppython Simulator.py' without quotes.


